# Project Context

This directory stores information that is not visible in code but should guide AI learning and checks. It is not a built-in prompt override directory; built-in prompts are maintained by skills-seed.

## Files

- `project.md`: business background, external systems, production facts, and hidden constraints.
- `rules.md`: long-lived team rules, compatibility requirements, security boundaries, and forbidden changes.
- `glossary.md`: domain terms, aliases, state names, and mappings between business language and code terms.

Use `--context` or `--context-path` for one-time guidance instead of writing it here.
